  infoPanel: {fileID: 1914681051}
  chapterTitle: 'Chatper 3 : The Detail'
  chapterText: 'Look closely  everything that matters is small. Beneath this glass
    I left the

    2nd truth, the one they''d never think to magnify. The safe,
    the device, the

    grand gestures were only theatre. The real proof was always
    in the details no

    one bothers to examine. Dr. A.'
  puzzleManager: {fileID: 962960528}
  puzzleIndex: 2
  requirePreviousChapter: 1
  lockedTitle: "Not yet\u2026"
  lockedMessage: There are earlier pages you haven't read. Piece the story together
    in order first.
