  infoPanel: {fileID: 1914681051}
  chapterTitle: 'Chapter 2 : The Light'
  chapterText: 'They came asking their questions, always at the 7th hour, always
    smiling. So

    every evening I lit this lamp, to make them believe I still
    slept here. I did

    not sleep. I sat behind the light, deciding how a man
    ends the thing he spent

    his life building. Dr. A.'
